    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    temperature DECIMAL,
    humidity DECIMAL,
    carbon_level DECIMAL

  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  temperature FLOAT,
  humidity FLOAT,
  location VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE environmental_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,

);

CREATE TABLE simulation_data (
    simulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    simulation_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE behavior_data (
    behavior_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,

    behavior_description TEXT,
    behavior_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
CREATE TABLE environment_data (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   location VARCHAR(255),   temperature FLOAT,   humidity FLOAT,   timestamp TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE user_preferences (   id INT PRIMARY KEY,   user_id INT,   eco_friendly_behavior BOOLEAN,   notifications_enabled BOOLEAN );
